channel.title: I cant log into my own server, but other people can get on it..wtf?
channel.description: Hi, today i offically released my server, The Forgotten Aeon. It seems very popular with other users. Yet..i cant log onto it myself! When i click login, it eventually comes up with the typical runescape but with a black screen saying loading-please wait. I wait for 10 minutes+ then my person shows up..connection lost...then the server crashes. WTF is going on?
